display="inline"><![CDATA[k\colon \mathbb {N}\times \mathbb {N}\to  A]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p>
 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[   k{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}} = e_{e_I{\mathopen {}\left (m\right )\mathclose {}}}{\mathopen {}\left (n\right )\mathclose {}}  ]]></fr:tex>

 <fr:p>The function <fr:tex
